{
  "texts": [
    "Thus, there are concrete actors which have a strong interest that progress in AI research continues unabated.",
    "In other words, there are strong commercial and geopolitical incentives to push forward with more AI research and those incentives are already entrenched in today's economy and politics.",
    "Thus, even if no actor aims at \"building AI which is capable of disempowering humanity\" (under this description) there are incentives to try to build AI which is as powerful as possible.",
    "Given the previous section, I expect that such AI would in fact be able to disempower humanity.",
    "Second, with sufficient time (e.g., by 2100), it looks like sufficiently powerful AI could be built by many different entities."
  ]
}